<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:21:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：中国禾赛明年将激光雷达价格减半，预计将在电动汽车中广泛采用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大的自动驾驶激光雷达传感器制造商中国禾赛集团表示，计划明年将其主要产品的价格削减一半，这将导致该技术在电动汽车中得到更广泛的采用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝评论被监禁官员薄熙来之子的婚姻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国周三拒绝就被监禁的前领导人薄熙来的儿子与台湾人的婚姻发表评论，只是表示反对对此事的“恶意”猜测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 04:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪表示已为供应商设定了可协商的降价目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-sets-negotiable-price-reduction-targets-suppliers-2024-11-27/</link><description>比亚迪一位高管周三表示，该公司在大规模采购时为供应商设定了降价目标，但这些目标是可以协商的，而不是强制性的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 04:29:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-sets-negotiable-price-reduction-targets-suppliers-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>由于特朗普关税担忧，亚洲股市走弱；日元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周三走高，因为投资者担心即将上任的美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能会针对哪些国家征收关税，一天前他承诺对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收新的关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国可能因总统太平洋访问而在台湾附近举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</link><description>根据台湾和地区安全官员的评估，中国可能会在未来几天在台湾附近发动军事演习，以总统赖清德即将前往太平洋和计划过境美国为借口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾富士康表示，全球制造足迹使其免受特朗普关税的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</link><description>台湾富士康周三表示，预计美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普征收新关税对公司的影响将小于其竞争对手，理由是其全球制造业足迹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:17:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道中国国防部长因腐败接受调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-defence-minister-placed-under-investigation-corruption-ft-reports-2024-11-27/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周三报道，中国国防部长董军已接受调查，这是一项范围广泛的反腐败调查的一部分，该调查已经扰乱了中国人民解放军高层。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 02:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-defence-minister-placed-under-investigation-corruption-ft-reports-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国10月工业利润小幅下滑，但逆风迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-industrial-profits-extend-decline-weak-demand-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国10月份工业利润再次下降，但降幅较上月有所下降，原因是通货紧缩压力拖累，而受危机打击的19万亿美元经济体的需求依然疲软。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 02:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-industrial-profits-extend-decline-weak-demand-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体警告特朗普不要发动相互破坏的关税战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-state-media-dismiss-trumps-tariff-vow-focus-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国官方媒体警告美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普承诺因芬太尼流通而对中国商品征收额外关税，可能会将世界最大的两个经济体拖入一场相互破坏的关税战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-state-media-dismiss-trumps-tariff-vow-focus-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国恒大投资者强烈抗议，敦促采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/careful-protest-china-evergrandes-investors-press-action-2024-11-27/</link><description>数百名因中国恒大倒闭而损失积蓄的中国投资者本月发起了一场协调一致的运动，向当局施压，要求提供这家倒闭房地产开发商的最新情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/careful-protest-china-evergrandes-investors-press-action-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普提议的关税可能如何影响大宗商品和能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/how-trumps-proposed-tariffs-might-affect-commodities-energy-2024-11-27/</link><description>当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周一承诺对美国三大贸易伙伴——加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税。拟议的关税将影响广泛的行业，包括石油、天然气、农业和制造业，有可能改变长期建立的贸易模式和供应链。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/how-trumps-proposed-tariffs-might-affect-commodities-energy-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普关税承诺扰乱货币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 21:49:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>出于安全考虑，中国警告新西兰不要加入 AUKUS - 报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-nz-against-joining-aukus-amid-security-concerns-report-2024-11-26/</link><description>中国驻新西兰大使王小龙表示，如果新西兰加入安全组织AUKUS，将“不可避免地”对该国与中国的关系产生负面影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 20:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-nz-against-joining-aukus-amid-security-concerns-report-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>分析师和商界领袖对特朗普的北美关税威胁做出反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/analysts-react-trumps-threat-north-american-tariffs-2024-11-26/</link><description>周二，金融分析师和商界领袖对美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁做出反应，特朗普将在 1 月份连任时对主要贸易伙伴墨西哥和加拿大征收 25% 的关税，此举可能引发贸易战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/analysts-react-trumps-threat-north-american-tariffs-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>员工称轩尼诗暂停在中国装瓶干邑白兰地的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-suspends-plan-bottle-cognac-china-say-staff-2024-11-26/</link><description>周二，听取管理层通报的员工表示，法国干邑制造商轩尼诗已暂停在中国装瓶白兰地的计划，以避免进口关税，此前数百名工人上周举行罢工抗议此举。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 14:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-suspends-plan-bottle-cognac-china-say-staff-2024-11-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>